{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-category-template-js","path":"/category/前端/page/1","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"nodes":[{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/03/object-oriented-program-design-principles-study","categorySlugs":["/category/前端/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"学习面向对象编程设计原则","date":"2020-03-31T10:46:37.121Z","categories":["前端"],"description":null,"featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/258d7644ee24d8cba17dcebcee780623/26dc0/featured_media.jpg","srcSet":"/static/258d7644ee24d8cba17dcebcee780623/26dc0/featured_media.jpg 1000w","sizes":"1000px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/258d7644ee24d8cba17dcebcee780623/abea9/featured_media.webp 1000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"1000px"}]},"width":1000,"height":547}}}},"excerpt":"在用 TypeGraphQL 和工具 TypeDI开发中，新接触到依赖注入(dependency inject)、抽象类(abstract class) 概念，这些概念的提出都源自于面向对象编程的设计原则(Object Oriented Program design principles)。找到几篇通俗易懂的文章，让我这个自学出生的程序员都能理解，记下这几篇优秀的文章，反复阅读理解之。"},{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/03/real-time-multi-device-collaboration-devtools","categorySlugs":["/category/前端/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"几款多端实时协作、同步的开发工具","date":"2020-03-22T10:46:37.121Z","categories":["前端"],"description":"在做一个消息列表同步时，使用 PubSub 模式针对各种场景补漏，代码越来越多且复杂难以维护。展开搜索，发现一些有用的工具","featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/010a7678366ffe60463c627ef7aa994c/ed3fb/featured_media.png","srcSet":"/static/010a7678366ffe60463c627ef7aa994c/ed3fb/featured_media.png 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/010a7678366ffe60463c627ef7aa994c/e7773/featured_media.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}}},"excerpt":""},{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/03/askent-give-up-prisma2","categorySlugs":["/category/前端/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"Askent 项目进展及准备弃用 Prisma2","date":"2020-0